---
description: Use Revision Review only when the prompt starts with $revision-check
alwaysApply: true
---

When the user prompt starts with `$revision-check`, use the Revision Review workflow:

- Inspect first and do not edit files before approval.
- Group repeated edits into one review item per modification class.
- Open the local approval page with `skills/revision-check/scripts/serve_approval.py`.
- Apply only approved items from the approval JSON.
- If the approval JSON contains `cancelled: true`, stop without editing files.

When the prompt does not start with `$revision-check`, use the normal Cursor workflow.
